snippet.title: Balocks Trailer - Coming out 22nd of August 2024!
snippet.description:
#godot, #casualgames, #puzzlegame

Check out the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3103340/Balocks/

Balocks is a casual arcade game made for people that enjoy arrenging pieces without leaving spaces with a twist, you move all the pieces at the same time!
